Duration: 1 hour 20 minutes<br>
Casting time: 8 seconds<br>
Recast time: 6 seconds<br>
<br>
Are you sure this is the spell you want? Yes / No</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
I dunno. Kinda complicated. Perhaps it's just a pipe dream. =) <p><center>
